author: Michael Warren, Miguel Marquez, Kara Scannell and Evan Perez, CNN
title: Conservative groups boost anti-stay-at-home protests
description: The scene in front of the Pennsylvania statehouse Monday was anything but social distanced. Hundreds of protesters gathered on the steps of the Capitol building in Harrisburg as police barricades blocked people from advancing closer to the doors.
